{
  "id": "RAW_ddf4320a",
  "title": "Agent 的技术瓶颈出现了？2026 年，Skills 才更重要！",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU2Njg0OTEyNQ==&mid=2247490668&idx=1&sn=895cf6cbd109aacf48b67f58ff81a343",
  "date": "2026-01-12 08:42:00",
  "author": "AI异类弗兰克",
  "siteName": "AI异类弗兰克",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.56298828125\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"2048\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100007011\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d404e3d8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F9CRQL8peAG0MUA7rFEVgCniayZic5bB2g3Biab5O658fibNFryicsnibMxh0OFngFDAmmuHFcSe596h7KaeJVkaoQMNQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">如果从技术演进的角度复盘最近一年的</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;Agent&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">项目，一个越来越清晰的事实是：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;\">问题正在从</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;\">“</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;\">模型够不够强</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;\">”</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;\">，转向</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;\">“</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;\">系统如何承载判断</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;\">”</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Claude</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">、</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">GPT&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这类模型在生成能力上已经高度成熟，至少在大多数工程场景中，</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">“</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">能不能生成</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">”</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">早已不是主要限制。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">真正开始拖慢系统演化速度的，是我们把大量本该被工程化、被结构化的判断，持续交给模型在运行时即兴完成。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这个问题在系统早期往往不明显。</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Agent&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">的第一个原型通常表现良好，一个</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;prompt</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">，加上一点工具调用，就能跑通完整流程。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但随着场景增多、上下文变复杂、需求开始叠加历史约束，系统会逐渐进入一种工程上非常危险的状态：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">行为开始变得不可预测，但你却很难准确定位问题发生在哪一层。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"What are Claude Skills and how can you use them for product-related work?\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.61015625\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2560\" data-imgfileid=\"100007006\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=17438adb&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F9CRQL8peAG0MUA7rFEVgCniayZic5bB2g3xfJY0pcJHrUtW4YtjcD0ictM0CsiaAlAkRNLjyv2OcBxpJTVRib6MIlaQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">模型参数没有变，数据来源也没有明显变化，业务逻辑看起来仍然成立，但结果却开始呈现出</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">“</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">有时对，有时不对</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">”</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">的不稳定特征。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">关键并不在于模型是否足够稳定，而在于系统结构是否在回避一个更基础的问题：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><b><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">哪些判断应该被固化为系统能力，哪些判断才值得在每一次调用中重新推理</span></span></b><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">当所有判断都被交给模型即时完成，系统规模越大，不确定性就会被放大得越快。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6212962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100007013\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=326e4a07&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F9CRQL8peAG0MUA7rFEVgCniayZic5bB2g3ibU0jtviagZ7OO0h6ZYiaDgeImYPSIpPicDZ1cicgpb1auvYxVP6QpPzicLQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">从这个角度再回头看</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;Claude Skills</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">，会发现它并没有试图解决</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">“</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">更强智能</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">”</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">的问题，而是在解决一个更底层、更工程化的难题：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">如何把已经被反复验证过的能力，从不透明的</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;prompt&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">行为中拆解出来，变成可管理、可复用、可回收的系统组件。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Skill&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">的价值，并不在于能力本身，而在于它让经验第一次具备了长期资产的形态。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100007014\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=412a2cc8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F9CRQL8peAG0MUA7rFEVgCniayZic5bB2g3DB26OGGczBhwG8FfWTzWQ3CRCst11BuZUF8FMKxMpXtu91lXNDCoaA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.337037037037037\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100007015\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=575733a4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F9CRQL8peAG0MUA7rFEVgCniayZic5bB2g311oxL8ia2ltAGSaibInHnGfice4CZCAvHI5eibMcOdNknicvFEwRxtJR7ibA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这也是为什么当系统里的</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;Skills&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">从十几个增长到几十个、上百个时，能力管理本身会迅速成为瓶颈。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">最近看到的</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;\">特赞科技&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;\">atypica.AI</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">发了一个</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1ODM1MjA3NQ==&amp;mid=2247484944&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=15d64102c5c70b1929834c92f75de7ac&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">skill0</span></a></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">( <a href=\"http://skill0.io/)\" target=\"_blank\">http://skill0.io/)</a></span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">，正是围绕这一问题给出的一个具体实践：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">当能力规模扩大，如何让不同团队知道哪些能力已经被验证、哪些仍处在试验阶段，以及如何避免在系统内部反复造轮子。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">如果缺少这样一层能力承载机制，所谓的</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;Agent&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">架构，最终很容易退化回</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;prompt&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">的堆叠。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100007016\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f462773f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F9CRQL8peAG0MUA7rFEVgCniayZic5bB2g3kWag3CFuYBQMaibEwa99M1JlsuMSVCkaVTic0A9pQJz061JiaSCJjoU9g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4888888888888889\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100007017\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=86f1ab58&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F9CRQL8peAG0MUA7rFEVgCniayZic5bB2g37fqxdvBpFf5gPJV5uR8Gp8VJX1WGlxJiarkPs1dIOut7j5GKnCO7pbw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;\">在这一过程中，</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;\">Agent&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;\">的角色也在悄然发生变化。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">与其让</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;Agent&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">承担越来越多</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">“</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">会做什么</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">”</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">的职责，不如让它回到一个更克制的位置：理解上下文、做路径选择、判断是否调用某种能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">执行的确定性尽可能被</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;Skills&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">吸收，不确定性才留给推理层处理。到这个阶段，系统关注的重点自然会从</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">“</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">输出是否漂亮</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">”</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">，转向</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">“</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">判断是否正确</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">”</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"What Is SKILL.md in Claude Skills? Structure, Resources &amp; Loading\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" data-imgfileid=\"100007004\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=017f3116&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F9CRQL8peAG0MUA7rFEVgCniayZic5bB2g3JGicPftgqNibL8jBg2hM1aqRnicQtz5MvC4u70XKmcAB4y3OMzeR98f1w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">从行业整体来看，这并不是某一家团队的独立选择，而是一种越来越普遍的工程收敛方向。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;\">当</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;Agent&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;\">真正进入复杂系统、长期运行环境之后，判断如何被工程化、被治理，正在取代模型能力本身，成为新的技术分水岭。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100007012\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d8a90f19&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F9CRQL8peAG0MUA7rFEVgCniayZic5bB2g3hXclTnXuVyueYI5wX3Jg4tTppZDnaeZGNpmTib6rTHbltZlgVVayr0w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章探讨了 Agent 技术从模型生成能力向系统工程化治理的转型，强调将判断逻辑固化为可管理的 'Skills' 是解决 Agent 不确定性瓶颈的关键。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章探讨了 Agent 技术从模型生成能力向系统工程化治理的转型，强调将判断逻辑固化为可管理的 'Skills' 是解决 Agent 不确定性瓶颈的关键。",
  "summary": "本文深度分析了当前 AI Agent 开发面临的技术瓶颈：过度依赖模型在运行时的即兴推理，导致复杂系统出现不可预测的不稳定性。作者提出，Agent 的演进方向正从“模型强度”转向“系统承载判断的能力”。核心观点是应将经过验证的经验从透明的 Prompt 堆叠中拆解出来，转化为结构化、可复用的 'Skills'（技能）组件。通过这种方式，执行的确定性由 Skills 吸收，而模型仅负责上下文理解与路径选择。文章还结合 Claude Skills 和 skill0.io 等实践，指出能力治理将成为未来复杂 Agent 系统的新技术分水岭。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Agent 的瓶颈已从模型生成能力转向系统如何承载判断。",
      "explanation": "目前模型生成能力已成熟，系统不稳定的根源在于将大量本该结构化的判断交给模型即兴完成，导致行为不可预测。"
    },
    {
      "point": "将判断固化为系统能力（Skills）是实现工程化稳定的关键。",
      "explanation": "通过将经验拆解为可管理、可复用的系统组件，让 Skills 吸收执行的确定性，从而降低系统规模扩大带来的风险。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Agent 的角色应回归到上下文理解与路径选择的克制位置。",
      "explanation": "与其让 Agent 承担所有职责，不如让其专注于推理层，而将具体的执行逻辑交给已验证的技能库，提高判断的正确率。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "真正开始拖慢系统演化速度的，是我们把大量本该被工程化、被结构化的判断，持续交给模型在运行时即兴完成。",
    "Skill 的价值，并不在于能力本身，而在于它让经验第一次具备了长期资产的形态。",
    "执行的确定性尽可能被 Skills 吸收，不确定性才留给推理层处理。",
    "判断如何被工程化、被治理，正在取代模型能力本身，成为新的技术分水岭。"
  ],
